{"tid":519882,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"惠理集團（00806）賣盤告吹","createTime":"2018-01-04T22:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T12:03:20.000Z","uid":26619,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce73838bc3d4098470f3984bef448c9ac825be7","tid":519882,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T22:42:14.000Z","msg":"「股壇金手指」謝清海旗下的惠理集團（00806）賣盤告吹。惠理去年5月宣布，有獨立第三方洽購集團主席謝清海及非執行名譽主席葉維義手上共41.04%的股份，當時市傳買家是海航集團，但惠理昨日宣布，謝清海及葉維義已終止與潛在收購方磋商，雙方並無訂立任何協議.....<br />\n<br />\n搞左惠理半年，同海航消息連一線，壓盤半年，最後唔買，所以我真係好憎大陸仔海航，以後都唔會搭香港航空。希望今次同條仆街斷關係，可以價值回歸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c7cd7503f9ea1e6ba5bb75999387be53f4fc97","tid":519882,"uid":26619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:49:34.000Z","msg":"近排真係行運。7.5有大貨。"},{"pid":"fcca230c2bc47ee8b548c28b8eb32305c3deee34","tid":519882,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>近排真係行運。7.5有大貨。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n竟然無連燈仔討論！"},{"pid":"8272dab2871f8abd0023b9702b1dc8af89135096","tid":519882,"uid":4425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:53:22.000Z","msg":"806 到而家仲係undervalued<br />\n<br />\n好彩我係臨大升之前買左d"},{"pid":"fd20e03ed794a51efe632c87a06352d0735487eb","tid":519882,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>806 到而家仲係undervalued<br />\n<br />\n好彩我係臨大升之前買左d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大戶都追緊貨，有得再升。"},{"pid":"cc329e151fcd84753e23ec43e0c8879d7145ad19","tid":519882,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:58:26.000Z","msg":"本來今朝放哂，睇來現在我都要再追貨。"},{"pid":"9b0ae9f2613d5fe252bd2b9a21edc552be78fa8f","tid":519882,"uid":4425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"等佢過兩日回一回翻先再入"},{"pid":"bc4faf265743b